Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.40,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.31,Main,Guardian,0,0,0,,Julian, why don’t I drop you off?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.15,0:00:34.44,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I’m good, I can walk.
