Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.94,0:01:29.98,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.73,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I didn’t call for a taxi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.15,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I told you I don’t want a taxi—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.85,0:02:01.90,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.90,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Wh-Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.44,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Hey— Gogoat?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.44,0:02:09.44,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Let me down!
Comment: 10,0:02:14.60,0:02:17.73,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.27,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Wow!
Comment: 10,0:02:25.52,0:02:26.27,Main,Oldman,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.85,0:02:36.77,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Wh—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.90,0:02:42.90,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.52,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,G—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.02,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Wh—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.56,0:02:59.02,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Comment: 10,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.81,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.44,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.02,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.98,0:03:49.19,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,...didn’t want to go to school,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.81,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,to be honest.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.81,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,My friend and me...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.48,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.69,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Take me somewhere even more fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.27,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I don’t want to...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.73,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,...go to school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.60,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.85,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Gogoat?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.94,0:04:29.69,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.23,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Lucas!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.02,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,Julian!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.69,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Sorry I’m late!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.52,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,All good, don’t worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.48,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.40,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,O-Ow...!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.10,0:05:50.60,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Ugh! What gives?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.60,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I’ve got to...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.81,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,...apologize to Lucas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.10,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Lucas...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.06,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.81,0:07:12.90,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,Julian!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.06,Main,Julian,0,0,0,,I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.73,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.19,Main,Julian & Lucas,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.56,Main,Lucas,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?! \N We’re gonna be late!
